    {
      "id": "37ea027b_18ce7930",
      "file_path": "components/pm-subscription-handler/pmsh_service/mod/api/services/measurement_group_service.py",
      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 229,
      "message": "Update looks good, But please have a look the below scenario\n\n--> Having 2 subscriptions A & B with 4 NF's as 1,2,3,4\n\nA matches NF's of 1,2 and 3\nB matches NF's of 1,2,3 and 4\n\nSo, if we UNLOCKED to LOCKED of sub B then 1,2 and 3 NF's won't be deleted due to relation is there with other's and NF 4 will be deleted. So, next time if we do LOCKED to UNLOCKED by this code we are missing NF 4 because if condition is satisfied with 1,2 and 3 NF's",
      "author": {
